4
00:02:13,571 --> 00:02:16,429
<i>Dobrodosli u Gatlin!</i>

5
00:02:27,128 --> 00:02:29,186
Jushua!

6
00:02:34,080 --> 00:02:36,480
Joshua!

7
00:02:44,560 --> 00:02:48,720
Decko... Ucinices ovu noc vrlo tuznom.

8
00:02:53,160 --> 00:02:55,880
Uhvaticu te.

9
00:03:16,080 --> 00:03:18,840
Eli?

10
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:22,600
Priblizava se.

11
00:03:22,760 --> 00:03:24,520
Pijan je, zar ne?

12
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:27,360
Opet ce me pretuci.

13
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:30,240
Nece ako se ja pitam.

14
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:32,120
Hajde, idemo.
-Idi!

15
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:35,000
Necu da te ostavim.

16
00:03:35,160 --> 00:03:39,760
Znas da sam jedini koji
moze da ga zaustavi.

17
00:03:39,920 --> 00:03:44,200
- Dobro. Ali budi tacno iza mene.
- OK.

18
00:03:58,080 --> 00:03:59,840
Zasto, tata?

19
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:02,680
Zasto moras povredjivati mog brata?

20
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:06,360
Porodica je svetinja tata.

21
00:04:07,640 --> 00:04:11,680
Znas da te ja nikada ne bih povredio.

22
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:16,040
Cak ni zbog ovog.

23
00:04:16,200 --> 00:04:19,200
Ti si uzeo.

24
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:32,440
Glupi klinac.

25
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:24,720
Cuvaj ovo, kao sto cuvas mene.

26
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:31,480
Eli.

27
00:05:31,640 --> 00:05:34,320
Rekao si da ces biti iza mene.

28
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:36,240
Gde je on.

29
00:05:36,400 --> 00:05:38,160
Hajde, idemo.

30
00:05:38,320 --> 00:05:41,960
Meni moze da radi sta hoce,
ali mu necu dozvoliti da tebe povredi.

31
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:43,880
Moramo ostati zajedno.
Zar ne?

32
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:46,800
Tako je.
Hajde, idemo.

33
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:08,240
Ovi momci ce biti smesteni u hraniteljsku porodicu,
sve dok papiri za usvojenje ne budu konacno zavrseni.

34
00:06:08,400 --> 00:06:11,120
Svasta su prosli, i morate
biti spremni da ...

35
00:06:11,280 --> 00:06:16,000
prodje neko vreme pre nego
sto se ne naviknu na novo okruzenje.

36
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:19,760
Ovi momci nikada nisu...
-Bili u gradu.

37
00:06:19,920 --> 00:06:23,640
Znam da znas i da si nervozan,
ali me saslusaj.

38
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:27,440
Zato sto je to jedini nacin...
-Cekajte, ovo su oni.

39
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:31,040
Pokusajte da budete prisebni.

40
00:06:47,760 --> 00:06:50,520
Izgledas prelepo.
-Hvala.

41
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:53,360
Previse si mlada da bi imala sina tinejdzera.
- Prestani!

42
00:06:53,520 --> 00:06:58,200
Williamie i Amanda!
Upoznajte vase momke.

43
00:06:58,360 --> 00:07:01,040
Zdravo, Eli. Josh.

44
00:07:01,200 --> 00:07:06,680
Dobrodosli u Chicago.
-Drago nam je sto ste ovde!

45
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:57,720
To je to!

46
00:07:57,880 --> 00:08:00,600
Dome, slatki dome...

47
00:08:00,760 --> 00:08:03,160
Spremni?

48
00:08:09,400 --> 00:08:11,120
Bas je lepo.

49
00:08:11,280 --> 00:08:13,080
Vece je od nase prikolice, zar ne Eli?

50
00:08:13,240 --> 00:08:17,560
Imate puno lepih stvari Gdjo Porter.

51
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:23,280
Hajdemo gore, pokazacu vam vasu sobu.

52
00:08:27,640 --> 00:08:30,760
Imamo decu u kuci!

53
00:08:32,480 --> 00:08:34,200
Ovo je nasa soba.

54
00:08:34,360 --> 00:08:37,080
Ako vam bilo sta treba,
mi smo par koraka dalje od vas.

55
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:41,880
Sve sto trazimo je da kucate pre nego udjete.

56
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:45,760
Joshua! Molim te, spusti to!

57
00:08:45,920 --> 00:08:48,600
Vrlo je skupo!

58
00:08:48,760 --> 00:08:50,520
Imate jako lepu kucu, Gosp Porter.

59
00:08:50,680 --> 00:08:53,440
Hvala Eli.
-Ovo je sada i tvoja kuca Eli.

60
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:58,080
Ne moras nas zvati gospodine i gospodjo, ok?

61
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:07,840
Josh, rekao sam ti da ga ne diras.

62
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:11,600
Bill, to je samo parce stakla!

63
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:16,440
Hajde, idemo.

64
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:19,120
Hajde.

65
00:09:29,120 --> 00:09:31,800
Jescemo najnoviji japanski izum.

66
00:09:31,960 --> 00:09:34,720
Mi to zovemo... pizza.

67
00:09:34,880 --> 00:09:36,640
Hvala, sedi.

68
00:09:36,800 --> 00:09:39,480
Hoces li da ti pomognem da je iseces?

69
00:09:39,640 --> 00:09:42,400
Pobogu, Amanda, moze i sam.

70
00:09:42,560 --> 00:09:46,640
Samo je podignes, savijes i smazes...

71
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:53,720
Molitva?

72
00:09:55,040 --> 00:09:56,800
Izvinjavam se.

73
00:09:56,960 --> 00:10:00,440
Hoces li ti da imas tu cast?

74
00:10:02,720 --> 00:10:06,360
Zahvalimo se Onome Koji Hoda Iznad Ruza...

75
00:10:06,520 --> 00:10:08,320
da cuva nase useve kukuruza,

76
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:11,200
a bezboznike i nevernike drzi...

77
00:10:11,360 --> 00:10:15,040
u vecnom ognju pakla zauvek.

78
00:10:15,200 --> 00:10:17,960
Amen.
- Amen.

79
00:10:19,040 --> 00:10:22,120
Ova je bila prosvetljujuca.

80
00:10:22,880 --> 00:10:25,240
Pizze?

81
00:10:26,720 --> 00:10:30,400
Podjite za mnom, pokazacu vam vase dvoriste.

82
00:10:30,560 --> 00:10:35,040
Ovo je Amandin Rajski vrt.
Jako je ponosna na njega.

83
00:10:35,360 --> 00:10:38,080
Gospodja iz socijalne sluzbe je rekla da imate kukuruz.

84
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:42,600
Stvarno?
Nemamo kukuruz.

85
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:45,760
A da, ja prodajem kukuruz!

86
00:10:45,920 --> 00:10:50,280
Ja sam trgovac na berzi.

87
00:10:51,680 --> 00:10:53,440
Sta je na drugoj strani?

88
00:10:53,600 --> 00:10:55,360
Stara napustena fabrika.

89
00:10:55,560 --> 00:11:01,120
Nije bas bezbedno, zato smo
napravili ovu ogradu ispred zida.

90
00:11:01,280 --> 00:11:05,240
Ali ne zelim da se vi igrate tamo.

91
00:11:07,040 --> 00:11:10,280
Gde je tvoj brat?

92
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:34,720
Ona hoce da mi oduzme loptu.

93
00:11:34,880 --> 00:11:37,400
Malcolm!

94
00:11:37,800 --> 00:11:40,960
On napada kos.

95
00:11:43,560 --> 00:11:47,200
Zdravo. Upravo sam se uselio u kucu pored vase.

96
00:11:47,360 --> 00:11:50,080
Kakva ti je to odeca?

97
00:11:50,280 --> 00:11:53,800
Je li to nesto amisko?

98
00:11:54,080 --> 00:11:58,760
Sta je sa tvojom kapom?
Zasto si je stavio naopacke?

99
00:11:58,920 --> 00:12:01,320
Joshua.

100
00:12:03,680 --> 00:12:06,440
Molim te, dodji kuci.

101
00:12:06,600 --> 00:12:09,000
Hvala.

102
00:12:24,840 --> 00:12:28,440
To je trebalo da bude iznenadjenje.

103
00:12:28,680 --> 00:12:30,400
Moras biti pazljiviji.

104
00:12:30,560 --> 00:12:33,320
Ne mozes tek tako prici stranicima i...

105
00:12:33,480 --> 00:12:35,960
William!

106
00:12:37,280 --> 00:12:40,040
Otvorila sam kofer, a unutra su bile bube.

107
00:12:40,200 --> 00:12:42,960
Sta?
-Otvori!

108
00:13:01,320 --> 00:13:04,160
Bube Amanda?

109
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:13,640
Pomislio sam da donesem ukus domaceg.

110
00:13:13,800 --> 00:13:16,760
To je lep kukuruz.

111
00:13:33,960 --> 00:13:35,720
Nije mi zgodno.

112
00:13:35,880 --> 00:13:37,640
Nismo vise sami.

113
00:13:37,800 --> 00:13:42,440
Samo se moramo navici.
-Mislis?

114
00:13:42,600 --> 00:13:45,320
Ne brini se.
Ucicemo u stos.

115
00:13:45,480 --> 00:13:47,280
I ionako Eli je jos mali...

116
00:13:47,440 --> 00:13:51,080
a Joshua treba malo discipline.

117
00:13:51,240 --> 00:13:54,240
Na kraju krajeva, treba i nama.

118
00:13:59,880 --> 00:14:02,600
Neces mi dati dok ne pogledamo momke jos jednom, zar ne?

119
00:14:02,760 --> 00:14:05,040
Da, odmah.

120
00:14:07,600 --> 00:14:09,960
Tiho.

121
00:14:20,040 --> 00:14:23,760
Sigurno su celog zivota spavali u istom krevetu.

122
00:14:23,920 --> 00:14:27,800
-Ostavimo ih na miru.
- Dobro.

123
00:14:43,120 --> 00:14:45,800
Ono sto sam danas uradio...

124
00:14:45,960 --> 00:14:48,720
vec sam sve zeznuo.

125
00:14:48,880 --> 00:14:51,600
Prvo sam ga naljutio zato sto sam
razbio figuru...

126
00:14:51,760 --> 00:14:55,440
a posle zato sto sam pricao sa strancima.

127
00:14:55,600 --> 00:14:58,320
Bar imamo jedan drugog.

128
00:14:58,480 --> 00:15:00,200
Tako je.

129
00:15:00,360 --> 00:15:02,920
Laku noc.

130
00:16:45,080 --> 00:16:49,640
Nudim ovo Onome Koji Hoda Iznad Ruza...

131
00:17:57,080 --> 00:17:58,840
David! Daj mi unapredjenje!
Ionako imam jos dvoje usta da hranim.

132
00:18:01,880 --> 00:18:04,600
Zato si se odlucio na usvojenje?

133
00:18:04,760 --> 00:18:07,480
Ma daj, ko je zakljucio ugovor sa Agrotehnom?
Ja sam.

134
00:18:07,640 --> 00:18:10,360
Ko je prodao kukuruz, kada niko
nije hteo da ga kupi? Ja sam.

135
00:18:10,520 --> 00:18:12,280
To zasluzuje neko priznanje, David.

136
00:18:12,440 --> 00:18:14,200
William, mnogo si nestrpljiv.

137
00:18:14,360 --> 00:18:17,080
Jednog dana, to ce te dovesti do nevolja.

138
00:18:17,240 --> 00:18:19,000
Opusti se, i uzivaj u novoj porodici.

139
00:18:19,160 --> 00:18:20,920
Berza nece ici nikuda.

140
00:18:21,080 --> 00:18:25,400
Berza mozda nece ici.
Ali ja hocu.

141
00:18:26,658 --> 00:18:27,170
Razmisli o tome.

142
00:18:33,600 --> 00:18:35,320
Ma da, ovo ti pristaje.
Sta mislis?

143
00:18:35,480 --> 00:18:37,240
A ovo?

144
00:18:37,400 --> 00:18:39,160
Svidje mi se kako ti stoji.
Definitivno tvoja boja.

145
00:18:39,320 --> 00:18:43,320
Cekaj da donesem makaze, da skinemo etikete.

146
00:18:53,982 --> 00:18:55,121
Dakle?

147
00:19:09,120 --> 00:19:12,760
Eli, samo sam...

148
00:19:16,800 --> 00:19:19,480
Ne svidja vam se garderoba koju sam kupila?

149
00:19:19,640 --> 00:19:24,320
Bez uvrede. Skromna garderoba je
jedan od puteva do vecnog zivota.

150
00:19:24,480 --> 00:19:29,120
Mislim, siguran sam da ne mogu svi
da priuste takvu garderobu u skoli.

151
00:19:29,280 --> 00:19:33,120
Zasto mi da ih ucinimo zavidnim?

152
00:19:35,040 --> 00:19:37,440
Dobro.

153
00:19:46,560 --> 00:19:48,320
Izvinite, kako da dodjem do
direktorove kancelarije?

154
00:19:48,480 --> 00:19:51,200
Naravno, na kraju hodnika,
pa levo.

155
00:19:51,360 --> 00:19:54,280
Druga vrata.
-Puno hvala, ovuda!

156
00:20:01,920 --> 00:20:03,640
Gospodja Porter?
- Amanda Porter.

157
00:20:04,956 --> 00:20:06,408
Ja sam otac Frank Nolan.

158
00:20:06,888 --> 00:20:08,072
Ovde sam direktor.
-Drago mi je!

159
00:20:08,684 --> 00:20:10,592
- Ovo mora da su momci?
- Tako je.

160
00:20:10,520 --> 00:20:13,240
- Joshua?
- Blizu. Eli.

161
00:20:13,400 --> 00:20:15,160
Joshua.

162
00:20:15,320 --> 00:20:18,720
Svidja mi se kosulja.

163
00:20:22,000 --> 00:20:23,760
Pokazacu vam vase ucionice.

164
00:20:23,920 --> 00:20:26,960
Ovuda.
-Hvala.

165
00:20:28,720 --> 00:20:31,440
Dobro jutro, razredu.

166
00:20:32,560 --> 00:20:34,280
Joshua. Ti si ovde, ucionica 101.

167
00:20:34,440 --> 00:20:36,200
To je moj razred.

168
00:20:36,360 --> 00:20:39,240
A Eli... u 112.

169
00:20:40,200 --> 00:20:41,960
Razdvajate nas?

170
00:20:42,120 --> 00:20:44,840
U razlicitim ste razredima.

171
00:20:45,000 --> 00:20:46,760
Oce, tamo odakle mi dolazimo...

172
00:20:46,920 --> 00:20:49,640
Joshua, znam sta hoces da kazes,
uvek ste bili zajedno...

173
00:20:49,800 --> 00:20:52,040
NE!

174
00:20:54,560 --> 00:20:57,280
Oce, mogu li da popricam sa vama napolju?
-Naravno.

175
00:20:57,440 --> 00:20:59,200
Bicemo napolju.

176
00:20:59,360 --> 00:21:03,320
Izvinite nas.
Izvadite knjige.

177
00:21:05,080 --> 00:21:07,480
Zdravo.

178
00:21:20,400 --> 00:21:22,160
Niko ne sedi tamo.

179
00:21:22,320 --> 00:21:24,920
A zasto?

180
00:21:25,240 --> 00:21:29,800
Zato sto mislim da ces mi popusiti kurac.

181
00:21:33,840 --> 00:21:37,680
Zar nemas usi, klinjo?
Hej, tebi govorim.

182
00:21:41,480 --> 00:21:45,880
Hoces malo ovoga?
- T-Loc. Bas si strasan.

183
00:21:46,320 --> 00:21:49,000
Sta ces da radis?
Da poseces decaka amisa?

184
00:21:49,160 --> 00:21:50,960
Posecicu tebe, kucko.

185
00:21:51,120 --> 00:21:52,840
Kome ti kucko? To moja sestra.

186
00:21:53,000 --> 00:21:57,640
Prebicu te sto tako pricas sa mojom sestrom.

187
00:21:57,800 --> 00:22:01,440
Odbij.
-Sta je covece? Ajde, navali?

188
00:22:01,600 --> 00:22:04,360
Nolan se vraca.

189
00:22:06,828 --> 00:22:08,663
Eli, zao mi je.

190
00:22:10,108 --> 00:22:11,400
Vidjacete se na odmorima.

191
00:22:46,640 --> 00:22:48,400
Zasto si ustao?

192
00:22:48,560 --> 00:22:50,320
To se tako radi.

193
00:22:50,480 --> 00:22:52,240
U daminom prisustvu?

194
00:22:52,400 --> 00:22:56,240
Isuse. Vidi se da nisi odavde.

195
00:22:57,160 --> 00:23:00,640
Cekas svoga brata?

196
00:23:04,419 --> 00:23:08,248
Slusaj to sto si uradio jutros je cool...

197
00:23:09,023 --> 00:23:09,803
Ali jako glupo.

198
00:23:11,286 --> 00:23:13,003
Ne zezaj se sa T-Lojem.

199
00:23:14,821 --> 00:23:15,953
On ne treba da se zeza sa Eli.

200
00:23:22,080 --> 00:23:24,440
Igras li?

201
00:23:26,880 --> 00:23:29,560
- Majmune?
-Sta je?

202
00:23:29,720 --> 00:23:31,480
Moze li Amis igrati?

203
00:23:31,640 --> 00:23:35,320
-Zasto?
-Zato sto sam ja tako rekla.

204
00:23:35,480 --> 00:23:39,400
Malcolm ne.
-Zasto? Neka igra.

205
00:23:46,926 --> 00:23:48,465
Znas li da igras?

206
00:23:49,738 --> 00:23:50,381
Malo.

207
00:23:51,606 --> 00:23:52,108
Dobro.

208
00:24:03,874 --> 00:24:04,825
To je malo?

209
00:24:15,061 --> 00:24:18,062
Hajde da ti pokazem kako se 
pozdravljamo posle dobrog poteza.

210
00:24:21,119 --> 00:24:21,897
Ne tako jako.

211
00:24:42,560 --> 00:24:45,160
Kakav kos.

212
00:24:52,120 --> 00:24:55,520
Izvini me, moram ici.

213
00:25:05,520 --> 00:25:09,200
Prvo me napustis,
a onda igras njihove igre.

214
00:25:09,360 --> 00:25:13,040
Samo sam se zabavljao.
Nisam imao izbora, morao sam te ostaviti.

215
00:25:13,200 --> 00:25:16,840
Rekli smo da cemo se drzati zajedno,
bez obzira na sve.

216
00:25:17,000 --> 00:25:21,800
Znas da hocemo.
-Onda nemoj igrati njihove igre.

217
00:25:22,760 --> 00:25:25,160
Molim te.

218
00:25:53,262 --> 00:25:54,623
<i>Divljine ce se naseliti...</i>

219
00:25:55,540 --> 00:25:56,778
<i>...pustinje ce procvetati...</i>

220
00:25:58,095 --> 00:26:00,904
<i>u ime Onoga Koji Hoda Iznad Ruza
i njegove dece...</i>

221
00:26:02,005 --> 00:26:03,321
<i>Mi smo Izabrani!</i>

222
00:26:03,993 --> 00:26:05,709
<i>...Samo mi..</i>

223
00:26:04,880 --> 00:26:06,640
<i>cemo naseliti zemlju..</i>

224
00:26:06,800 --> 00:26:08,560
<i>...u domovima..</i>

225
00:26:08,720 --> 00:26:10,520
<i>...u hodnicima i ucionicama...</i>

226
00:26:10,680 --> 00:26:12,400
<i>...igralistima...</i>

227
00:26:11,736 --> 00:26:13,608
<i>Sve dok nevernici ne osete nas bes...</i>

228
00:26:14,187 --> 00:26:16,425
<i>Nasu odmazdu koju cemo prosuti pred njih...</i>

229
00:26:16,891 --> 00:26:18,190
<i>Napunicemo zemlju sa njima...</i>

230
00:26:19,132 --> 00:26:22,892
<i>Mi smo seme, i sada je doslo vreme...</i>

231
00:26:23,323 --> 00:26:23,736
<i>...da narastemo.</i>

232
00:26:27,004 --> 00:26:29,703
<i>Svi nevernici koji predju preko njega...</i>

233
00:26:30,481 --> 00:26:35,138
<i>...bice svareni...</i>

234
00:26:40,043 --> 00:26:42,543
BLAGOSLOVI MOJE SRCE!

235
00:26:56,950 --> 00:26:57,525
Sta se desava?

236
00:27:00,166 --> 00:27:01,957
Sta se desilo ovde?

237
00:27:43,560 --> 00:27:46,360
Isuse Hriste.

238
00:28:48,720 --> 00:28:51,240
Alleluja.

239
00:28:56,320 --> 00:28:58,080
Zasto odbijas da me saslusas?

240
00:28:58,240 --> 00:29:00,040
Necu da se svadjam oko polja kukuruza.

241
00:29:00,200 --> 00:29:01,960
Zar ti njie palo na pamet da...
-Ako ti neces da ga poseces...

242
00:29:02,120 --> 00:29:08,640
Poseci cu ga sama.
-Amanda to mu je hobi.

243
00:29:15,520 --> 00:29:18,200
To je ludost.

244
00:29:18,360 --> 00:29:20,120
Dobro.

245
00:29:20,280 --> 00:29:23,680
Pogledacu ga ujutro.

246
00:29:49,040 --> 00:29:51,360
Isuse.

247
00:30:01,480 --> 00:30:03,840
Ima li koga?

248
00:30:06,280 --> 00:30:08,640
Halo.

249
00:30:11,040 --> 00:30:12,800
Uplasio sam te, zar ne?

250
00:30:12,960 --> 00:30:14,720
Bas jesi.

251
00:30:14,880 --> 00:30:16,640
Dosao si da zanjes?

252
00:30:16,800 --> 00:30:19,520
Nisam, ali da hocu, mogao bih.
Gospode, pogledaj ga.

253
00:30:19,680 --> 00:30:21,440
Da, hoces da probas?

254
00:30:21,600 --> 00:30:24,040
Naravno.

255
00:30:28,280 --> 00:30:31,600
Sladko mirise.
-Da.

256
00:30:40,720 --> 00:30:43,440
Eli. Odakle ti ovo?

257
00:30:43,600 --> 00:30:46,320
Od mog oca.

258
00:30:46,480 --> 00:30:48,240
Neka mu je laka crna zemlja.

259
00:30:48,400 --> 00:30:50,200
On je razvio ovaj tip.

260
00:30:50,360 --> 00:30:53,040
Moze se reci da sam
mu ja pomogao.

261
00:30:53,200 --> 00:30:54,960
Ovo je od nekolicine klipova.

262
00:30:55,120 --> 00:30:58,760
Doneo sam ih iz Gatlina,
da vidim mogu li ovde uspeti.

263
00:30:58,920 --> 00:31:01,640
Pa uspevaju, moj Boze!

264
00:31:01,800 --> 00:31:05,240
A nije cak ni sezona...

265
00:31:05,640 --> 00:31:08,360
Ovo zemljiste je uzasno neplodno.

266
00:31:08,520 --> 00:31:10,320
Nema djubriva.

267
00:31:10,480 --> 00:31:13,120
Nema insekata.

268
00:31:13,280 --> 00:31:17,960
Eli, ovo si uzgajio u
samo cetiri nedelje?

269
00:31:18,120 --> 00:31:21,760
Imas li ti predstavu koliko ovo
seme moze vredeti?

270
00:31:21,920 --> 00:31:25,640
Pa... kako je moj otac uvek govorio...

271
00:31:25,800 --> 00:31:29,360
Zanjes ono sto posijes.

272
00:31:53,560 --> 00:31:56,400
Lepo mirise.

273
00:32:10,800 --> 00:32:13,360
Dovidjenja.

274
00:32:29,000 --> 00:32:30,680
Dobro.

275
00:32:30,840 --> 00:32:35,800
Kako to da nam se tvoj
brat nikada ne pridruzi?

276
00:32:36,640 --> 00:32:39,960
Izvinite me.

277
00:32:44,320 --> 00:32:47,000
Zasto si to rekao?

278
00:32:47,160 --> 00:32:48,920
Zdravo Eli.

279
00:32:49,080 --> 00:32:50,840
Hoces li da dodjes kod nas?

280
00:32:51,000 --> 00:32:53,720
Zasto se ti meni ne pridruzis?

281
00:32:53,880 --> 00:32:57,520
Ili bi radije jeo... sa tim?

282
00:33:00,560 --> 00:33:01,360
To, Eli, je prijatelj!

283
00:33:01,520 --> 00:33:03,280
Znas?

284
00:33:03,440 --> 00:33:08,880
Ne bi skodilo ni kada bi ti imao prijatelje.

285
00:33:09,200 --> 00:33:12,200
Mozda i hocu...

286
00:34:36,600 --> 00:34:41,640
Moje sluzenje danas je iz Jovana 37.

287
00:34:42,360 --> 00:34:45,120
Jovan je sanjao san...

288
00:34:45,280 --> 00:34:47,040
I rekao je svom svesteniku...

289
00:34:47,200 --> 00:34:48,920
I mrzeli su ga zbog toga...

290
00:34:49,080 --> 00:34:54,320
Toliko su ga mrzeli da su prodali
svog bliznjega u belo roblje...

291
00:34:54,840 --> 00:34:59,280
A njegovom ocu rekli da je mrtav...

292
00:35:00,600 --> 00:35:03,320
Jovan je video viziju istine...
- Joshua.

293
00:35:03,480 --> 00:35:08,080
Mi ucimo iz ovoga, da oni koji...
- Joshua. Na desno.

294
00:35:08,240 --> 00:35:10,000
Cesto ce se susresti sa opovrgavanjem...

295
00:35:10,160 --> 00:35:13,840
Od Neznalica i Zlobnih...

296
00:35:14,000 --> 00:35:15,760
Hocu da sklopim prijateljstva!

297
00:35:15,920 --> 00:35:18,720
Eli Porter!!!

298
00:35:23,600 --> 00:35:25,360
Da li ti je moje sluzenje dosadno?

299
00:35:25,520 --> 00:35:28,160
Jeste Oce!

300
00:35:29,360 --> 00:35:32,080
Ako mislis da mozes bolje...

301
00:35:32,240 --> 00:35:38,040
zasto se ne popnes ovde gore,
i podelis svoje misli sa nama?

302
00:35:39,880 --> 00:35:42,800
Hvala Oce!

303
00:35:43,720 --> 00:35:45,480
Ko je bio Jovan?

304
00:35:45,640 --> 00:35:48,680
Kome je dodjavola stalo?

305
00:35:49,520 --> 00:35:51,840
Meni.

306
00:35:53,280 --> 00:35:55,080
A trebalo bi da je i vama.

307
00:35:55,240 --> 00:35:58,920
Zato sto je on bio dete, bas kao i mi.

308
00:35:59,080 --> 00:36:02,800
Dete sa velikom vizijom o svetu.

309
00:36:02,960 --> 00:36:04,680
Jer, Jovan je voleo zemlju...

310
00:36:04,840 --> 00:36:07,520
Koja je donosila hranu za nase stomake...

311
00:36:07,680 --> 00:36:09,480
Drvo za nasa sklonista...

312
00:36:09,640 --> 00:36:13,280
Okeane za igru i vazduh da nas odrzi.
- Eli!

313
00:36:13,440 --> 00:36:18,120
Ali on nije primetio tu grupu,
koja je oskrnavila Majku Zemlju...

314
00:36:18,280 --> 00:36:21,880
Koja je otrovala zemlju sa pesticidima
i posekla sume kao travu!

315
00:36:22,040 --> 00:36:23,840
Eli!

316
00:36:24,000 --> 00:36:28,600
Zagadila vazduh i zatrovala vodu sa kanalizacijom.

317
00:36:28,760 --> 00:36:32,080
A ko je bila ta grupa?

318
00:36:32,680 --> 00:36:34,400
To su bila braca...

319
00:36:34,560 --> 00:36:37,760
Njegova odrasla braca...

320
00:36:38,400 --> 00:36:42,040
Jovan nije hteo to da im dozvoli!

321
00:36:42,200 --> 00:36:46,600
A ne trebate ni vi!
-Dosta!

322
00:36:47,040 --> 00:36:49,600
Dosta!

323
00:36:50,880 --> 00:36:54,240
U moju kancelariju. Odmah.

324
00:37:11,960 --> 00:37:17,080
Ako si spreman da se izvinis,
bicu u svojoj ucionici.

325
00:37:17,720 --> 00:37:19,480
Nije vam se svidelo sluzenje?

326
00:37:19,640 --> 00:37:24,240
Ne zanima me nista sto
imas da kazes sada.

327
00:37:24,400 --> 00:37:27,680
To dolazi u supi.

328
00:37:34,000 --> 00:37:36,720
Nisi mi rekao da je
tvoj brat propovednik.

329
00:37:36,880 --> 00:37:39,560
Ma da, pokupio je to od svog oca.

330
00:37:39,720 --> 00:37:42,440
Hoces da kazes "od mog oca"?

331
00:37:42,600 --> 00:37:44,400
Ne, njegovog.

332
00:37:44,560 --> 00:37:46,320
Izvini, mislio sam da sam ti rekao.

333
00:37:46,480 --> 00:37:50,160
Njega su usvojili.

334
00:37:50,320 --> 00:37:53,040
Dobro vece, gdjo Porter.
Ovde Samantha Gordon iz socijalne sluzbe.

335
00:37:53,200 --> 00:37:55,880
Gledala sam stara dokumenta,
i nasla sam neke iz Gatlina.

336
00:37:56,040 --> 00:37:58,760
I moze se reci, da je vezano za Eli.

337
00:37:58,920 --> 00:38:03,560
Mozete li me nazvati, cim cujete
ovu poruku? Hvala!

338
00:38:03,720 --> 00:38:06,440
Halo. Halo.

339
00:39:04,120 --> 00:39:05,880
Sranje.

340
00:39:06,040 --> 00:39:10,680
Koliki grad a nema osvetljenja...

341
00:39:10,840 --> 00:39:12,600
Dodjavola...

342
00:39:12,760 --> 00:39:16,040
Gde li je nestao?

343
00:39:16,600 --> 00:39:19,360
Ovo trazis?

344
00:39:30,000 --> 00:39:33,680
Dobili ste Cikago policiju...

345
00:39:33,840 --> 00:39:39,720
Molim vas, ostanite na liniji,....
DOK TE PRVI SLOBODAN NE UBIJE...

346
00:40:04,520 --> 00:40:08,200
Imajte odlican dan, momci!
-Hvala.

347
00:40:08,360 --> 00:40:11,800
A ja necu dobiti poljubac?

348
00:40:12,240 --> 00:40:15,760
Naravno.

349
00:40:18,920 --> 00:40:21,640
Zdravo, mama.

350
00:40:37,120 --> 00:40:39,840
Gospodine Porter, vasa zena je na liniji...

351
00:40:40,000 --> 00:40:41,800
Na sastanku sam!
-Rekla je da je hitno!

352
00:40:41,960 --> 00:40:45,360
Onda joj recite da sam izasao.

353
00:40:45,760 --> 00:40:52,240
Oseti strukturu, kao da je fabricki.
Mekan je na dodir, ali tako tvrd da ga ne mozes slomiti...

354
00:41:07,800 --> 00:41:10,360
Taj kuckin sin.

355
00:41:14,520 --> 00:41:18,200
Ako Wiliam nece, poseci cu ga sama...

356
00:41:18,360 --> 00:41:23,000
Imam dobre vesti,
neki od vas ce proci...

357
00:41:23,160 --> 00:41:26,840
Ne ti, Jenkins. Ti neces nikada proci.

358
00:41:27,000 --> 00:41:30,720
Slusaces ovaj razred sledece godine i one tamo ponovo.

359
00:41:30,880 --> 00:41:34,480
Ne znas ni koja je najduza reka u USA.

360
00:41:34,640 --> 00:41:36,440
Odakle je doslo?

361
00:41:36,600 --> 00:41:39,320
Ma daj, Charles. Znas i bolje.

362
00:41:39,480 --> 00:41:41,200
Zamisli se.

363
00:41:41,360 --> 00:41:45,080
Otporan na insekte i pesticide.

364
00:41:45,240 --> 00:41:50,800
Skraceno vreme od sejanja do zetve.

365
00:41:50,960 --> 00:41:54,920
U rukama drzis bogatstvo, Charles.

366
00:41:59,600 --> 00:42:02,320
Zasto tajis ovo?
Ovo je veliko.

367
00:42:02,480 --> 00:42:05,200
Zasto bi ovo podelio sa mojim poslodavcima?

368
00:42:05,360 --> 00:42:07,120
Ja sam ga razvio.

369
00:42:07,280 --> 00:42:09,040
Znam, ali eticki...

370
00:42:09,200 --> 00:42:11,920
Zajebi etiku!

371
00:42:12,080 --> 00:42:14,560
William.

372
00:42:14,960 --> 00:42:17,680
Ovo je prvi put da te cujem da psujes.

373
00:42:17,840 --> 00:42:23,360
I zapamtite, postoje samo dva planinska lanca u USA.

374
00:42:36,000 --> 00:42:38,560
Sranje!

375
00:43:09,560 --> 00:43:11,320
William!!!

376
00:43:11,480 --> 00:43:17,120
Charles. Poteban mi je investitor.
Znam da postoje i drugi kojima se mogu obratiti.

377
00:43:17,280 --> 00:43:21,120
Imam li tvoj glas na odboru ili ne?

378
00:44:04,240 --> 00:44:06,960
Izvinite!

379
00:44:07,160 --> 00:44:11,400
-Da, Eli?
-Mogu li da pijem vode?

380
00:44:12,840 --> 00:44:15,280
Mozes.

381
00:44:34,960 --> 00:44:36,720
Oce Frank.

382
00:44:36,880 --> 00:44:39,560
Kakva tragedija.

383
00:44:39,720 --> 00:44:44,560
Zovi nas ako ti treba nesto.

384
00:45:57,440 --> 00:46:00,440
Zetva se blizi!

385
00:46:08,880 --> 00:46:10,680
Dobar dan!

386
00:46:10,840 --> 00:46:13,480
Zdravo James.

387
00:46:13,640 --> 00:46:16,080
Zdravo.

388
00:46:16,600 --> 00:46:19,320
Zdravo Jonathan.

389
00:46:19,480 --> 00:46:21,880
Daniel.

390
00:46:23,320 --> 00:46:25,640
Gary.

391
00:46:26,200 --> 00:46:28,880
Dobro jutro.

392
00:46:30,000 --> 00:46:32,720
Rekao sam monsignoru, da sam

393
00:46:32,880 --> 00:46:34,600
osecao potrebu da promenim cas engleskog,

394
00:46:34,760 --> 00:46:39,560
ako zelimo da dospemo do
ciljeva koje smo naumili.

395
00:46:40,560 --> 00:46:42,280
I gorece u vecnom ognju pakla...

396
00:46:42,440 --> 00:46:46,880
A ovi prevaranti, izdajice, oni znaju ko su.

397
00:46:54,960 --> 00:46:57,680
Izvinite me.

398
00:46:58,800 --> 00:47:02,440
Slusaj Josh. Znam da se
Eli ponekad cudno ponasa...

399
00:47:02,600 --> 00:47:06,280
... ali slusala sam ga dok govori i
mnogo toga ima smisla.

400
00:47:06,440 --> 00:47:08,200
Maria! Ne!

401
00:47:08,360 --> 00:47:10,080
Samo se drzi podalje od njega!

402
00:47:10,240 --> 00:47:12,040
Veruj mi, ne znas na sta je sve sposoban.

403
00:47:12,200 --> 00:47:15,200
O cemu pricas?

404
00:47:16,000 --> 00:47:17,760
Sta nije u redu?

405
00:47:17,920 --> 00:47:20,760
Pogledaj ovo.

406
00:47:24,640 --> 00:47:28,320
Nasao sam to jutros ispod njegovog kreveta.

407
00:47:28,480 --> 00:47:30,280
Isuse...

408
00:47:30,440 --> 00:47:33,120
Znam da ti je brat, ali
zasto to ne pokazes nekom.

409
00:47:33,280 --> 00:47:36,000
William ce ga poslati psihijatru.

410
00:47:36,160 --> 00:47:37,920
-Mogao bi pokazati Ocu Nolan.

411
00:47:38,120 --> 00:47:41,600
-Ne. Ne mogu.
Zasto da ne?

412
00:47:41,920 --> 00:47:44,640
-Zato sto smo braca.
-Usvojena braca.

413
00:47:44,800 --> 00:47:49,400
Maria slusaj.
Eli i ja smo dosta toga preziveli.

414
00:47:49,560 --> 00:47:54,200
Uvek smo pazili jedan na drugog.
Mozda se oseca bezbedno.

415
00:47:54,360 --> 00:47:58,880
Osecas se bezbedno sa Malcolm-om?

416
00:47:59,200 --> 00:48:02,120
- Da.
A samnom?

417
00:48:16,440 --> 00:48:18,160
-Sta je bilo?

418
00:48:18,320 --> 00:48:22,000
-Nisam nikad ovo radio.

419
00:48:22,160 --> 00:48:24,760
Jednostavno je.

420
00:48:30,800 --> 00:48:33,920
Ovo je prva baza...

421
00:48:41,360 --> 00:48:44,080
Ovo je druga baza...

422
00:48:59,560 --> 00:49:01,360
-A kako da postignem HomeRun?

423
00:49:01,520 --> 00:49:04,360
-Nikako.

424
00:49:12,960 --> 00:49:14,760
Malcolm, Ma hajde covece!
Ja i Maria...

425
00:49:14,920 --> 00:49:17,640
....smo samo prijatelji!
- Ne. Ne razumes.

426
00:49:17,800 --> 00:49:19,560
Ona je moja sestra, ok?

427
00:49:19,720 --> 00:49:21,480
Recimo to ovako:

428
00:49:21,640 --> 00:49:25,320
Necu da se petlja sa porodicom
kao sto je tvoja.

429
00:49:25,480 --> 00:49:27,240
-A posebno sa tvojim poremecenim bratom!

430
00:49:27,400 --> 00:49:31,080
-Eli? Kakve on ima veze sa bilo cime?

431
00:49:31,240 --> 00:49:33,960
Ne budi glup!
Osvrni se oko sebe.

432
00:49:34,120 --> 00:49:37,760
Napusteno je,
a trebalo bi biti krcato, posle skole.

433
00:49:37,920 --> 00:49:39,680
Da te pitam nesto:

434
00:49:39,840 --> 00:49:43,280
Sta mislis sa kime su?

435
00:49:43,680 --> 00:49:45,440
Odlazim odavde.

436
00:49:45,600 --> 00:49:47,320
Sa godinama dolazi slepilo.

437
00:49:47,480 --> 00:49:50,240
Ali mi koji smo mladi-

438
00:49:50,400 --> 00:49:53,080
/mi smo cuvari vizije cistote/

439
00:49:53,240 --> 00:49:56,960
/To je, dar Onog Koji Hoda Iza Redova...

440
00:49:57,120 --> 00:50:02,720
/Tako da postujemo njegovu
volju, da ocistimo svet/

441
00:50:02,880 --> 00:50:04,640
Nasa zetva pocinje.

442
00:50:04,800 --> 00:50:08,440
Sta je ovo, mamu ti!

443
00:50:10,520 --> 00:50:12,280
-Zdravo.

444
00:50:12,440 --> 00:50:16,120
-Nemoj ti meni zdravo.

445
00:50:16,280 --> 00:50:19,360
Dosli smo po Dee.

446
00:50:22,080 --> 00:50:25,680
-Ne mogu da ga pustim.
-I sta ces onda da uradis?

447
00:50:25,840 --> 00:50:27,600
-Da mi propovedas do smrti?!

448
00:50:27,760 --> 00:50:30,640
-Proveri.

449
00:50:31,640 --> 00:50:34,880
Dolazi ovamo, seronjo mali!

450
00:50:39,280 --> 00:50:42,240
Ima da te polomim.

451
00:50:45,040 --> 00:50:48,360
Gde si, dupeglavac?

452
00:50:48,880 --> 00:50:50,680
-Sada si ovde samnom.
-Nisam ovde s tobom.

453
00:50:50,840 --> 00:50:54,800
-Ti si ovde samnom.

454
00:50:56,560 --> 00:50:59,840
Jebote! Sad si mrtav...!

455
00:51:03,280 --> 00:51:06,440
Skloni ga od mene,
skloni ga od mene!

456
00:51:08,080 --> 00:51:10,560
Pomozi mi! Pomozi mi!
Pomozi mi! Pomozi mi!

457
00:51:13,800 --> 00:51:15,560
Mogu da ti pomognem. Pitanje je,

458
00:51:15,720 --> 00:51:18,480
hoces li ti da pomognes meni?

459
00:51:18,640 --> 00:51:22,280
Hocu! Skloni ga od mene...!

460
00:51:22,440 --> 00:51:25,520
Hajde da se pomolimo.

461
00:51:25,418 --> 00:51:30,041
<i>/Video sam andjela, kako silazi
iz Raja noseci kljuc.../</i>

462
00:51:31,012 --> 00:51:35,411
<i>/...od rupe bez dna,
i veliki lanac u ruci/</i>

463
00:51:37,486 --> 00:51:42,822
<i>I sa time zakljucujem svoje
propovedanje o Otkrovenjima.</i>

464
00:51:47,398 --> 00:51:49,681
<i>DA LI IKO IMA NEKO PITANJE!!!!</i>

465
00:52:21,920 --> 00:52:26,560
Frank, pitas me za misljenje.
Zadnjih par nedelja, nije bilo...

466
00:52:26,720 --> 00:52:30,360
-pusenja u toaletima, tuca po

467
00:52:30,520 --> 00:52:34,200
hodnicima, nema droge i nozeva...

468
00:52:34,360 --> 00:52:38,040
-Stvari se konacno popravljaju.
-Popravljaju u sta? -U nesto dobro.

