484
00:53:52,674 --> 00:53:56,024
-Zdravo.

485
00:53:56,844 --> 00:53:57,516
-Zdravo i tebi.

486
00:53:58,313 --> 00:53:59,108
Ne spavas.

487
00:54:00,378 --> 00:54:01,237
-Radis naporno?

488
00:54:01,943 --> 00:54:04,358
-Pravim neke beleske za sutra ujutru.

489
00:54:05,187 --> 00:54:06,644
Lenje ruke su djavolje orudje.

490
00:54:07,270 --> 00:54:11,607
