507
00:57:12,409 --> 00:57:13,341
Paket za Amanda Porter.

508
00:57:14,836 --> 00:57:17,680
-Nije ovde.

509
00:57:21,080 --> 00:57:24,480
-Mozes li potpisati umesto nje.

510
00:57:27,760 --> 00:57:30,160
Hvala.

511
00:57:44,759 --> 00:57:45,631
Malcolm!

512
00:57:46,739 --> 00:57:47,629
