zetveni meseci.

540
00:59:23,834 --> 00:59:24,389
Video si ga nekad?

541
00:59:26,680 --> 00:59:30,320
-Ne. -Veceras pogledaj
u nebo i videces.

542
00:59:30,480 --> 00:59:33,200
