vidimo Oca Nolana.

543
00:59:33,360 --> 00:59:35,120
-Ko si ti?

544
00:59:34,614 --> 00:59:35,462
Oce.

545
00:59:36,597 --> 00:59:37,548
- Ti kao da ne znas?

546
00:59:39,306 --> 00:59:41,654
-Zasto idemo da vidimo Nolana?

547
00:59:42,022 --> 00:59:44,284
-Cuo sam nesto u menzi, mislim da razume.

548
00:59:53,520 --> 00:59:57,200
Primetili ste me.

549
00:59:57,360 --> 01:00:00,040
