550
01:00:00,200 --> 01:00:02,920
Neki ljudi to mogu, Frank.

551
01:00:03,080 --> 01:00:04,840
Ne znam zasto.

552
01:00:05,000 --> 01:00:08,240
Zaustavicu te!

553
01:00:09,840 --> 01:00:12,600
Naravno, Frank.

554
01:00:13,057 --> 01:00:14,593
Da vidim sta mozes.

555
01:00:19,199 --> 01:00:20,225
Zao mi je.

556
01:00:27,080 --> 01:00:28,840
-Ko si ti?!

557
01:00:29,000 --> 01:00:31,800
-Hajde da se pomolimo.

558
01:00:55,840 --> 01:00:59,560
