565
01:01:35,788 --> 01:01:36,274
Oce.

566
01:01:36,915 --> 01:01:37,877
Nije ovde.

567
01:01:38,437 --> 01:01:39,500
- Idemo u kapelu.

568
01:01:42,140 --> 01:01:42,813
Dragi Frank.

569
01:01:44,111 --> 01:01:44,581
Hvala!

570
01:01:45,896 --> 01:01:48,321
Hvala ti sto
si poziveo dovoljno-

571
01:01:48,560 --> 01:01:50,280
