575
01:01:58,836 --> 01:01:59,633
Sa ovim?

576
01:02:01,040 --> 01:02:02,800
Tvoja biblija nije dorasla mojoj.

577
01:02:02,960 --> 01:02:05,680
-Pokazi mi, i videcemo.

578
01:02:05,840 --> 01:02:08,240
-Frank, Frank, Frank...

579
01:02:08,720 --> 01:02:14,320
