01:05:14,720 --> 01:05:17,640
Dome, slatki dome.

609
01:05:44,267 --> 01:05:45,520
Mislim da je ostavio kod strasila.

610
01:05:47,416 --> 01:05:48,255
-Kojeg strasila?

611
01:05:50,121 --> 01:05:51,464
-Ti uzmi ono desno, a ja cu levo.

612
01:06:02,313 --> 01:06:05,056
